\c 8
\s Indaba yowesifazana weShunemi
\p
\v 1 UElisha wasekhuluma kowesifazana ondodana yakhe ayeyenze yaphila\x + 4.35.\x*, esithi: Sukuma, uhambe wena lendlu yakho, u\add ye\add*hlala njengowezizwe lapho ongahlala khona njengowezizwe, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ibize indlala, ezafika njalo elizweni iminyaka eyisikhombisa\x + 4.38. Hlab. 105.16. Hag. 1.11. Gen. 41.27. 1 Kho. 17.1. Seb. 11.28.\x*.
\v 2 Owesifazana wasukuma-ke, wenza njengokutsho komuntu kaNkulunkulu; wahamba yena lendlu yakhe, wahlala njengowezizwe elizweni lamaFilisti iminyaka eyisikhombisa.
\v 3 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kweminyaka eyisikhombisa, owesifazana waphenduka evela elizweni lamaFilisti; waphuma uku\add ya\add*khala enkosini ngendlu yakhe langensimu yakhe.
\v 4 Inkosi yayikhuluma-ke loGehazi inceku yomuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + 4.12.\x* isithi: Akungilandisele izinto zonke ezinkulu uElisha asezenzile.
\v 5 Kwasekusithi esatshela inkosi ukuthi wavusa njani ofileyo\x + 8.1.\x*, khangela-ke, owesifazana ondodana yakhe ayeyivuse ekufeni wakhala enkosini ngendlu yakhe langensimu yakhe. UGehazi wasesithi: Nkosi yami, nkosi, nguye lo owesifazana, njalo yiyo le indodana yakhe uElisha ayiphilisayo.
\v 6 Lapho inkosi ibuza owesifazana, wayilandisela. Inkosi yasimmisela induna ethile, isithi: Buyisela konke okwakungokwakhe, laso sonke isivuno sensimu kusukela mhla esuka elizweni kuze kube lamuhla.
\s UHazayeli uba yinkosi yeSiriya
\p
\v 7 UElisha wasefika eDamaseko\x + 1 Kho. 11.24.\x*, njalo uBenihadadi inkosi yeSiriya wayegula\x + 1 Kho. 20.2.\x*. Wasetshelwa kwathiwa: Umuntu kaNkulunkulu ufikile lapha.
\v 8 Inkosi yasisithi kuHazayeli\x + 1 Kho. 19.17.\x*: Thatha esandleni sakho isipho, uyehlangabeza umuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 9.7.\x*, ubusubuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngaye usithi: Ngizasila yini kulumkhuhlane?
\v 9 UHazayeli wasesiyamhlangabeza, wathatha isipho esandleni sakhe, ngitsho esakho konke okuhle kweDamaseko, imithwalo yamakamela engamatshumi amane, weza wema phambi kwakhe, wathi: Indodana yakho uBenihadadi inkosi yeSiriya ingithumile kuwe isithi: Ngizasila yini kulumkhuhlane\x + 5.13.\x*?
\v 10 UElisha wasesithi kuye: Hamba uthi kuye: Ungasila lokusila, kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* ingibonisile ukuthi uzakufa lokufa\x + 8.15.\x*.
\v 11 Wase\add m\add*joloz\add el\add*a waze waba lenhloni. Umuntu kaNkulunkulu waselila\x + 2.17.\x*.
\v 12 UHazayeli wasesithi: Inkosi yami ililelani? Wasesithi: Ngoba ngiyazi ububi ozabenza ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli; uzathungela inqaba zabo ngomlilo, ubulale amajaha abo ngenkemba\x + 10.32. 12.17. 13.3,7,22. Amos 1.3.\x*, uphahlaze abantwanyana babo\x + Isa. 13.16. Hos. 13.16. Nah. 3.10. Hlab. 137.9. Hos. 10.14.\x*, uqhaqhe abesifazana babo abakhulelweyo\x + 15.16. Hos. 13.16. Amos 1.13.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa uHazayeli wathi: Kodwa iyini inceku yakho eyinja \add nje\add*, ukuthi yenze linto enkulu\x + 2 Sam. 3.8.\x*? UElisha wasesithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* ingibonisile ukuthi uzakuba yinkosi phezu kweSiriya\x + 1 Kho. 19.15.\x*.
\v 14 Wasesuka kuElisha weza enkosini yakhe eyathi kuye: UElisha utheni kuwe? Wasesithi: Ungitshele ukuthi uzasila lokusila\x + 8.10.\x*.
\v 15 Kwasekusithi kusisa wathatha ingubo, wayigxamuza emanzini, wayendlala phezu kobuso bakhe waze wafa. UHazayeli wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\s Ukubusa kukaJoramu koJuda
\p
\v 16 Njalo ngomnyaka wesihlanu kaJoramu indodana kaAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 1.17.\x*, lapho uJehoshafathi eyinkosi yakoJuda, uJehoramu indodana kaJehoshafathi inkosi yakoJuda waba yinkosi\x + 2 Lan. 21.1,3,4.\x*.
\v 17 Wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lambili lapho esiba yinkosi, wabusa iminyaka eyisificaminwembili eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 21.5-10.\x*.
\v 18 Wasehamba ezindleleni zamakhosi akoIsrayeli njengokwenza kwendlu kaAhabi, ngoba indodakazi kaAhabi yayingumkakhe; wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 8.26. 9.2.\x*\nd*.
\v 19 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* kayithandanga ukuchitha uJuda ngenxa kaDavida inceku yayo, njengokuthembisa kwayo kuye ukuthi izanika isibane kuye zonke izinsuku\x + 2 Sam. 7.12,13. Hlab. 132.11.\x*, \add l\add*emadodaneni akhe\x + 2 Lan. 21.7.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Ensukwini zakhe iEdoma yahlamuka isuka phansi kwesandla sakoJuda, yabeka inkosi phezu kwayo\x + 3.9. 1 Kho. 22.47.\x*.
\v 21 UJoramu wasewelela eZayiri lazo zonke inqola zilaye; yena wavuka ebusuku watshaya amaEdoma ayemzingelezele, lenduna zezinqola; labantu babalekela emathenteni abo\x + 2 Sam. 18.17.\x*.
\v 22 Ngakho iEdoma yahlamuka isuka phansi kwesandla sakoJuda kuze kube lamuhla. Khona iLibhina yahlamuka ngalesosikhathi\x + Josh. 10.29. 2 Lan. 21.10.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJoramu, lakho konke akwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda?
\v 24 UJoramu waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa kuboyise emzini kaDavida\x + 2 Lan. 21.20.\x*. UAhaziya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Lan. 22.1-6.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaAhaziya koJuda
\p
\v 25 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lambili kaJoramu indodana kaAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli uAhaziya indodana kaJehoramu, inkosi yakoJuda, waba yinkosi\x + 9.29.\x*.
\v 26 UAhaziya wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lambili lapho esiba yinkosi, wabusa umnyaka owodwa eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguAthaliya, indodakazi kaOmri inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Lan. 22.2.\x*.
\v 27 Wasehamba ngendlela yendlu kaAhabi, wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, njengendlu kaAhabi, ngoba wayengumkhwenyana wendlu kaAhabi\x + Gen. 19.14.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Wasehamba loJoramu indodana kaAhabi ukulwa loHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya\x + 8.15.\x* eRamothi-Gileyadi\x + 1 Kho. 22.3.\x*; amaSiriya aselimaza uJoramu.
\v 29 UJoramu inkosi wabuyela ukwelatshwa\x + 9.15.\x* eJizereyeli amanxeba amaSiriya ayemtshaye wona\x + Josh. 17.16.\x* eRama ekulweni kwakhe loHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya. UAhaziya indodana kaJehoramu inkosi yakoJuda wasesehla ukubona uJoramu indodana kaAhabi eJizereyeli, ngoba wayegula\x + 9.16.\x*.